			subtitle: "When supplied with power, the Powered Lantern will emita light source similar to Glowstone. However, it will keep mobs from spawning in a 32x32 area around them. The Floodlight, when provided with power will light an area of 32 blocks in front of it. With an Engineer's Hammer, you can rotate the Floodlight around. A redstone signal will be required to turn the Floodlight on. This behavior can be reversed with a Screwdriver"
